Track Nuvo state.

Event callback to receive all the dataclasses created from received nuvo
messages.
Stores each one in memory, merging any changes received.
{
    'ZoneStatus': {
        1: dataclass',
        2: dataclass,
        ...
    }
    'ZoneConfiguration': {
        1: dataclass',
        2: dataclass,
        ...
    }
}
